708
00:46:23,050 --> 00:46:24,550
<font color="#dfdf00">ඒ මොකක්ද?</font>

709
00:46:24,560 --> 00:46:26,460
<font color="#dfdf00">අපේ ලමයි ටික වගේ.</font>

